es/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/20px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/20px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sea_Lab\" title=\"Sea Lab\"><img alt=\"Sea Lab\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sea_Lab.png?fc048f\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sea_Lab\" title=\"Sea Lab\">Sea Lab</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/20px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Maker_3000\" title=\"Ice Maker 3000\"><img alt=\"Ice Maker 3000\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice_Maker_3000.png?5edeee\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Maker_3000\" title=\"Ice Maker 3000\">Ice Maker 3000</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/20px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Quacken_Drill\" title=\"Quacken Drill\"><img alt=\"Quacken Drill\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Quacken_Drill.png?c8845a\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Quacken_Drill\" title=\"Quacken Drill\">Quacken Drill</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/20px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Smelter\" title=\"Smelter\"><img alt=\"Smelter\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Smelter.png?c99738\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Smelter\" title=\"Smelter\">Smelter</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/20px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Oscillating_Fan\" title=\"Oscillating Fan\"><img alt=\"Oscillating Fan\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Oscillating_Fan.png?eab1aa\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Oscillating_Fan\" title=\"Oscillating Fan\">Oscillating Fan</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/20px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Accomploshrine\" title=\"Accomploshrine Console Editions only\"><img alt=\"Accomploshrine Console Editions only\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Accomploshrine.png?93fa63\" width