  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve|Reign of Giants|Shipwrecked|Hamlet}}\n{{for|the filter in [[Don't Starve Together]]|Prototypers & Stations Filter}}\n[[File:Icon Science.png|right|thumb|Tab Icon]]\n{{Quote|I am one heck of a scientist.|Wilson}}\nThe '''Science Tab''' allows the player to [[Crafting|craft]] scientific [[Item]]s and [[Structure]]s. It is displayed as the Atom icon on the left-hand side of the screen.\n\n==[[File:Gift Icon.png|32px]] Downloadable Content==\nIn the ''[[Reign of Giants]]'' DLC, [[Electrical Doodad]]s and [[Ice Flingomatic]]s were introduced to the Science Tab. They are available to craft in all [[DLC]]s.\n\nIn the ''[[Shipwrecked]]'' DLC, [[Sea Lab]]s, [[Ice Maker 3000]]s and [[Quacken Drill]]s were added to the Science Tab. Many Structures in this tab can be [[flooding|flooded]].\n\nThe ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC adds [[Smelter]]s and [[Oscillating Fan]]s to this tab.\n\n== Craftable Items and Structures ==\nThe following items and structures can be crafted from the Science Tab:\n\n<div style=\"clear:both; font-weight: bold\"><gallery columns=\"6\" position=\"center\" widths=\"70\" captionalign=\"center\" captionsize=\"medium\" bordersize=\"none\" spacing=\"medium\" hideaddbutton=\"true\" captionposition=\"below\" navigation=\"true\">\n\nScience Machine.png|link=Science Machine|[[Science Machine]]\nAlchemy Engine.png|link=Alchemy Engine|[[Alchemy Engine]]\nDivining Rod.png|link=Divining Rod|[[Divining Rod]]<br/>{{Pic|20|Don't Starve icon|Don't Starve}}\nThermal Measurer.png|link=Thermal Measurer|[[Thermal Measurer]]\nRainometer.png|link=Rainometer|[[Rainometer]]\nGunpowder.png|link=Gunpowder|[[Gunpowder]]\nLightning Rod.png|link=Lightning Rod|[[Lightning Rod]]\nElectrical Doodad.png|link=Electrical Doodad|[[Electrical Doodad]]<br/>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nIce Flingomatic.png|link=Ice Flingomatic|[[Ice Flingomatic]]<br/>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nSea Lab.png|link=Sea Lab|[[Sea Lab]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nIce Maker 3000.png|link=Ice Maker 3000|[[Ice Maker 3000]]<br/>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nQuacken Drill.png|link=Quacken Drill|[[Quacken Drill]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}\nSmelter.png|link=Smelter|[[Smelter]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nOscillating Fan.png|link=Oscillating Fan|[[Oscillating Fan]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}\nAccomploshrine.png|link=Accomploshrine|[[Accomploshrine]]<br/>Console Editions only\n</gallery></div>\n\n{{Tabs}}\n__NOTOC__\n[[ko:과학 탭]]"
}
